      <a href="/blog/jual-asxone-138-sl-pangkalan-banteng" class="hover-lift bg-green-50 hover:bg-green-100 rounded-xl px-4 py-3 text-green-800 font-medium transition text-center text-sm">📍 Pangkalan Banteng</a>
